fields.name: DelegatedIdentityClientId
fields.description: delegated identity to use for accessing key encryption key Url. Ex: /subscriptions/fa5fc227-a624-475e-b696-cdd604c735bc/resourceGroups/<resource group>/providers/Microsoft.ManagedIdentity/userAssignedIdentities/myId. Mutually exclusive with identityType systemAssignedIdentity and userAssignedIdentity - internal use only.

fields.name: IdentityType
fields.description: Values can be systemAssignedIdentity or userAssignedIdentity

fields.name: UserAssignedIdentityResourceId
fields.description: user assigned identity to use for accessing key encryption key Url. Ex: /subscriptions/fa5fc227-a624-475e-b696-cdd604c735bc/resourceGroups/<resource group>/providers/Microsoft.ManagedIdentity/userAssignedIdentities/myId. Mutually exclusive with identityType systemAssignedIdentity and delegatedResourceIdentity.
